Package jProtocol.tls12.model.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TlsAsymmetricOperationException
    An exception used for errors during asymmetric operations.
    TlsBadPaddingException
    An exception used for bad padding errors during decryption.
    TlsBadRecordMacException
    An exception used for bad record MAC errors during decryption.
    TlsDecodeErrorException
    An exception used for decoding errors during parsing a received message.
    TlsException  
    TlsInvalidCipherSuiteException
    An exception used for errors when requesting an invalid cipher suite.
